## Notes

Who or what is Himon?

> Himon is a citizen of New Genesis who secretly lives on the planet Apokolips, which is ruled by Darkseid.
>
> More details at [Himon (New Earth)](<https://dc.fandom.com/wiki/Himon_(New_Earth)>)

